                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "Assumptions followed by Semi-Supervised Learning"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "textStyle",
                "attrs": {
                  "color": ""
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "A Semi-Supervised algorithm assumes the following about the data"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "attrs": {
          "tight": true,
          "start": 1,
          "type": null
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Continuity Assumption:"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "textStyle",
                        "attrs": {
                          "color": ""
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": " The algorithm assumes that the points which are closer to each other are more likely to have the same output label."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Cluster Assumption:"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "textStyle",
                        "attrs": {
                          "color": ""
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": " The data can be divided into discrete clusters and points in the same cluster are more likely to share an output label."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Manifold Assumption:"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "textStyle",
                        "attrs": {
                          "color": ""
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": " The data lie approximately on a manifold of a much lower dimension than the input space. This assumption allows the use of distances and densities which are defined on a manifold."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Applications of Semi-Supervised Learning"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "attrs": {
          "tight": true,
          "start": 1,
          "type": null
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Speech Analysis:"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "textStyle",
                        "attrs": {
                          "color": ""
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": " Since labeling audio files is a very intensive task, Semi-Supervised learning is a very natural approach to solve this problem."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Internet Content Classification:"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "textStyle",
                        "attrs": {
                          "color": ""
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": " Labeling each webpage is an impractical and unfeasible process and thus uses Semi-Supervised learning algorithms. Even the Google search algorithm uses a variant of Semi-Supervised learning to rank the relevance of a webpage for a given query."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Protein Sequence Classification:"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "textStyle",
                        "attrs": {
                          "color": ""
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": " Since DNA strands are typically very large in size, the rise of Semi-Supervised learning has been imminent in this field."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
